== APRA Music Awards ==
The [[APRA Awards (Australia)|APRA Awards]] are several award ceremonies run in Australia by [[Australian Performing Right Association]], which includes the APRA Music Awards, to recognise composing and songwriting skills, sales and airplay performance by its members annually.

