| 2013 || "[[Suit & Tie]]" <small>(with [[Jay Z]])</small> || rowspan=2| Best Music Video || {{nom}} || <ref>https://camerimage.pl/en/nominacje-do-konkursu-wideoklipow/</ref>
|-
| 2018 || "[[Say Something (Justin Timberlake song)|Say Something]]" <small>(with [[Chris Stapleton]])</small> || {{nom}} || <ref>{{Cite news |url=https://camerimage.pl/nominacje-w-konkursie-wideoklipow-4/ |title=Nominacje W Konkursie Wideoklipow |work=Camerimage |access-date=October 3, 2018 |location=Poland}}</ref>
{{end}}

